# TypeDoc reference output target.
#
# This directory is populated by `npm run docs:reference` (see
# tooling/typedoc/typedoc.json). Track A's docs app (apps/docs/**) reads the
# generated HTML and surfaces it under /reference/<package>/.
#
# Generated HTML is not committed to main — CI uploads it as an artifact.
# The initial PR ships one sample package tree so the layout is visible.
